{"tid":1018134,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【豬年劏房頭炮】深水埗AVA 228最細129呎 市區最細新盤","createTime":"2019-02-12T04:21:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-12T05:34:27.000Z","uid":1550,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a7c0d2ba629076f2b142ccfecea239b69d2c9e90","tid":1018134,"uid":1550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T04:21:52.000Z","msg":"踏入豬年，首個上載樓書的新盤，最細單位不足130方呎，為豬年劏房市場打響頭炮。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【樓市成交】青衣樓價天與地 翠怡花園一個月貴一球<br />\n<br />\n資深投資者盧華家族旗下的深水埗大南街228號新盤AVA 228，剛上載樓書。單位總數160伙，一梯八伙，主打不足300呎迷你戶，間隔有開放式及一房，實用面積最大249方呎。<br />\n<br />\n最細為2樓D及E室特色戶，實用面積僅129方呎，另設28方呎平台，成新例後市區最細新盤。市區對上一個最細新盤同出自盧華家族的AVA系列，2015年開售的尖沙嘴AVA 62，最細單位152方呎。四年後AVA劏房系列更上一層樓，AVA 228單位面積已不足130方呎，再縮水15%，只比屯門「龍床盤」菁雋128方呎略大一呎。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【新盤消息】深水灣徑8號一組客5.2億購兩伙<br />\n<br />\n從平面圖所見，該「市區龍床盤」可謂入屋後一眼睇晒，129呎主要由三個部份組成，入屋後的走廊位已佔去約25呎，浴室可以用「豆腐膶咁大」形容，連坐廁及淋浴區僅約20呎。客飯廳約60方呎，若連同平台的28方呎，基本上活動空間不足90方呎，比赤柱單人囚室約80方呎還要細。發展商曾指，AVA 228最細單位面積是100多方呎，相信受上車客及投資者歡迎。項目屬遠期樓花，關鍵日期為2021年12月31日。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190211/59246953\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190211%2F59246953&d=DoGI4G7aG2aFCjNgNSWIunljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=3431140c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190211%2F59246953&h=acf5fb87\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190211/59246953</a>"},{"pid":"1e9559814a551d0f8661c6e87aec974be88207b7","tid":1018134,"uid":1550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T04:24:44.000Z","msg":"沒有最細只有更細<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似要破紀錄越整越細<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11b6c73b54cc438555716f40ec5cb59a186c3acd","tid":1018134,"uid":209301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T04:39:53.000Z","msg":"AV<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cc2fc7a252f192d4a70fe8760e420b728cf0b34","tid":1018134,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T04:40:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"016318771f84ce335a2087f723a834937c7b5666","tid":1018134,"uid":119330,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T04:42:42.000Z","msg":"樓價20萬 我屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97521c3f57dc8c3a46683b46fdada746cc7af670","tid":1018134,"uid":219277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T04:47:32.000Z","msg":"個廳仲細過我間房<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bd9aa319129ca3fbcaa9fe4fa5b2ca4e75be32f","tid":1018134,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T04:47:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eb4378a6a2fc8382748754d17b0db576157de4db","tid":1018134,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T05:27:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"62802993409ce286cba5be45c9132f11c90e57e1","tid":1018134,"uid":19287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T05:34:27.000Z","msg":"做一樓一<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}